ygData.messageBody:
I think two level 19's could make it.. .cause
you're druid... so therefore if you go .. you take
Butcherblock to Firona Vie and then keep killing at Lake of
Ill Omens...<br><br>There's plenty to kill it's just
it will be dangerous to run all the way to LoiO. And
you will be a mite underpowered. I've seen ppl around
level 19 yelling for groups all the time there
though... <br><br>As far as the SK suggestion... that's
what I did... I killed a bit in Highpass and SK at
aviak city for a good long while before I headed to
Kunark. That's actually a pretty good time all the way
from 18 to 23. At which time, I grabbed my ring spells
and headed to Kunark. I have my bind point in FV.
=)<br><br>shooman out<br>Fatedhue Prismatic on the Drinal Server.
